content: I'm going to reach out to Bob's Watches and Matthew Bain to see if they can find a Seamaster 2913 for me. I'll also set up alerts on 1stdibs and Chrono24 to notify me when a new listing becomes available. Additionally, I'll post a wanted ad on the Vintage Omega Collectors forum and the Omega Forums to see if anyone has a lead on a Seamaster 2913.
